## gram-cracker
A node.js n-gram extraction plugin.

[![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/jfuehner/gram-cracker.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/jfuehner/gram-cracker)

## Dependencies
The plugin is dependent upon [q](https://github.com/kriskowal/q) and [Underscore](http://underscorejs.org).

Unit tests are dependent upon [Mocha](http://visionmedia.github.io/mocha/) and [Should](https://github.com/visionmedia/should.js/).

## Usage
```
var gram_cracker = require("gram-cracker");

var gram = new gram_cracker();
gram.addDocuments([
        "The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog.",
        "Being bounced around quickly annoyed the disheveled taxi drivers."
    ])
    .then(function(docs) {
        var stopWords = ["a", "the"];
        
        gram.extract(2, stopWords).then(function(ngrams) {
            
            console.log(ngrams);
        });                
    });
```

